processingCommand.script:
! Will set only that accounts that are defined
:SET &WMS_CHANGE#      = "false"
:SET &REFS_CHANGE#     = "false"
:SET &EMS_CHANGE#      = "false"

:IF &WMS_DB_USERNAME# <> ""
:  IF &WMS_DB_USERNAME# <> "N/A"
:    SET &WMS_CHANGE# = "true"
:  ENDIF
:ENDIF

:IF &REFS_DB_USERNAME# <> ""
:  IF &REFS_DB_USERNAME# <> "N/A"
:    SET &REFS_CHANGE# = "true"
:  ENDIF
:ENDIF

:IF &EMS_DB_USERNAME# <> ""
:  IF &EMS_DB_USERNAME# <> "N/A"
:    SET &EMS_CHANGE# = "true"
:  ENDIF
:ENDIF

:PUBLISH &WMS_CHANGE#,,WORKFLOW
:PUBLISH &REFS_CHANGE#,,WORKFLOW
:PUBLISH &EMS_CHANGE#,,WORKFLOW
